org.energy_home.jemma.javagal.layers
Class PropertiesManager

java.lang.Object
  org.energy_home.jemma.javagal.layers.PropertiesManager
Deprecated. 

@Deprecated
public class PropertiesManager
extends java.lang.Object

Properties manager class. Loads/saves from/to a ".properties" file the desired values for JavaGal execution. It's THE way to control a number of parameters at startup.

Author:
"Ing. Marco Nieddu or from Consoft Sistemi S.P.A., financed by EIT ICT Labs activity SecSES - Secure Energy Systems (activity id 13030)"
